1
00:00:05,480 --> 00:00:06,610
Where are you going?

2
00:00:06,920 --> 00:00:08,160
I'll go get two more outfits.

3
00:00:08,160 --> 00:00:09,120
Then we can take a few more photos.

4
00:00:09,120 --> 00:00:09,800
Think about it.

5
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:12,640
The more we take, the more leverage we have, right?

6
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:14,320
Hurry up.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,200
Wear this.

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Wear this.

9
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,640
Don't be nervous. I'm just taking a few photos.

10
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,680
It's so simple.

11
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:33,880
I won't take photos.

12
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:36,040
Come here.

13
00:00:40,120 --> 00:00:41,580
Can I just not take photos?

14
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:45,060
Why wouldn't you take photos?

15
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:46,680
Damn.

16
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:49,000
It's not that I won't.

17
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,240
I want you to take them for me.

18
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,600
I don't want to undress in front of them.

19
00:00:58,040 --> 00:01:01,120
Then let's just take photos.

20
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,860
As long as you let me go,

21
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,320
I'll do anything.

22
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,600
I'll do anything.

23
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,600
That was satisfying.

24
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:34,400
I did everything you asked.

25
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,720
Can you let me go now?

26
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:38,920
Let you go?

27
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,800
You make me feel so good.

28
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:45,680
How could I bear to let you go?

29
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:51,560
Let's do it again later.

30
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,520
Help!

31
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,400
Come back!

32
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,570
Are you messing with me?

33
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,400
Speak.

34
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,360
Stop pretending.

35
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,120
Boss.

36
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,120
She...

37
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,120
This... this was an accident.

38
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,200
An accident?

39
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,450
An accident, right?

40
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,160
An accident!

41
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,560
An accident!

42
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,020
How many times have I told you?

43
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:17,960
You made him angry again.

44
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,520
I have to lecture you all day.

45
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,360
All right.

46
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,160
Enough.

47
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,120
You're going to beat him to death.

48
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,520
Listen to me. She ran out by herself.

49
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,400
I just pulled her.

50
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,320
She accidentally fell.

51
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:25,840
It really was an accident.

52
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,520
Why won't you believe me?

53
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,720
Don't panic.

54
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,200
I got the money.

55
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,720
So, you can let me go now, right?

56
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,720
Originally, yes.

57
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,400
I'm sorry, Na.

58
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,000
We had a little accident.

59
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,930
And we might need your help.

60
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,040
What help?

61
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,880
Maybe what I promised you yesterday...

62
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,200
I can't do it anymore.

63
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,320
What do you mean?

64
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,010
What are you going to do?

65
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,480
Lao San killed Linda.

66
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:35,680
If she doesn't die, we will.

67
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:42,650
You said you only wanted money, not lives.

68
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,600
I gave you all the money.

69
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,840
Why do you have to kill someone?

70
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:47,640
Jiajia.

71
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:51,480
Jiajia, my daughter is still so young.

72
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,280
You know, she...

73
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:55,680
How will she live without me?

74
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,120
Please don't kill me, okay?

75
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,920
I... listen, I swear.

76
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,880
I swear to God.

77
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,370
I won't tell anyone.

78
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,680
I won't tell a soul.

79
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,800
I won't say a word.

80
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,280
I won't tell.

81
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,040
I... no!

82
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:09,720
What are you doing?

83
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,200
Don't kill me!

84
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,000
Let go!

85
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,000
Didn't you promise not to kill anyone?

86
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,320
Let go!

87
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,240
Jiajia.

88
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,160
Let go!

89
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,920
Let go.

90
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,560
Let go.

91
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,640
Let go!

92
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,840
Let go.

93
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,360
I have no choice.

94
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,320
And neither do you.

95
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,640
Mom, I'm back.

96
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,920
Why are you back so early?

97
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:26,140
Isn't your factory working night shifts recently?

98
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,280
Who bought this TV?

99
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,680
Mr. Wang sent it.

100
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,840
This TV

101
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,740
and this new washing machine.

102
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:36,880
We won't have to worry from now on.

103
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:39,560
There aren't many people so sincere.

104
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,320
We need to hold the wedding soon.

105
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:46,440
Wedding? Me? With Mr. Wang?

106
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,080
I've only met him once.

107
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:51,640
And you've already accepted the betrothal gifts?

108
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,960
What are you talking about?

109
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,080
He took a fancy to you,

110
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,240
so it's settled.

111
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,880
How much money did he give in total?

112
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:01,080
20,000 in cash.

113
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:04,360
Plus the three major items and other odds and ends,

114
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,840
it's at least tens of thousands.

115
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,480
So much money.

116
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:01,040
I left the money for my mom.

117
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,120
What?

118
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:08,360
Your remaining money is enough for us to leave.

119
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:12,160
That's barely anything.

120
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,520
Are you crazy?

121
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:16,960
San.

122
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,480
You said I'd manage your money from now on.

123
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,960
Does that still count?

124
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:30,720
It counts.

125
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,980
No, it doesn't! What right does she have?

126
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,820
I'll help you guys earn more money in the future.

127
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,520
Just you?

128
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:44,560
How are you going to earn it?

129
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,970
Someone thinks she's really good at selling.

130
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,160
Lao San.
